revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
<!-- Place categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata -->
{{Tracks Wikidata|P18}}

'''{{NAMESPACE}}:{{BASEPAGENAME}}''' may be added to an [[Help:Infobox|infobox]] template which displays an image. In any article using the infobox with an image, it adds either {{cl|Articles having same image on Wikidata and Wikipedia}} or {{cl|Articles having different image on Wikidata and Wikipedia}}. In any article using the infobox without an image, it adds {{cl|No local image but image on Wikidata}} (also used by [[Template:Wikidata image]]).

== Usage ==
Add the following to a template (if necessary, change "image" to whatever parameter name that template uses to display an image):

:<code><nowiki>
{{compare|local={{{image|}}}}}
</nowiki></code>

== Tracking categories ==
* {{Category link with count|Articles having same image on Wikidata and Wikipedia}}
* {{Category link with count|Articles having different image on Wikidata and Wikipedia}}
* {{Category link with count|No local image but image on Wikidata}}

== Infoboxes using this template ==
* {{tl|Infobox aviator}}
* {{tl|Infobox beauty pageant}}
* {{tl|Infobox deity}}
* {{tl|Infobox religious biography}}
* {{tl|Infobox spy}}

== See also ==
* {{tl|Wikidata image}}

